Cell["\<\
Final size check.

The final contracted numerator is stored in the variable theOutput. We \
inspect its length to record the number of top-level additive terms in the \
resulting expression.

The value reported by Length[theOutput] is not the number of algebraically \
independent tensor structures. It is only a practical measure of the size of \
the expanded symbolic expression returned by the staged contraction.\
\>", "Text",
 Editable->False,
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.986354484910437*^9},ExpressionUUID->"0be16396-231d-47b3-a40e-\
64c7e973e72b"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"Length", "[", "theOutput", "]"}]], "Input",
 Editable->False,
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9863540932828813`*^9, 3.986354095902327*^9}, {
  3.98635412961486*^9, 3.98635413150438*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[18]:=",ExpressionUUID->"3527ba27-f9de-488b-9311-877dc3452485"],

